</head>
<body>

<div class="container-fluid content-box-show row" style="padding-left:5vw; padding-right:5vw;">
  <div class="row" style="  min-height: 760px; border:solid 1px; margin-top:107px; background-color:#191919; padding:60px;">

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="row">
        <div id="shown-img" class="img-responsive" style="background-color:white; height:550px; width:550px;"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <!--<div class="show-event-content">
        <h1 class="event-name"><b><%= @event.name %></b></h1>
        <p><%= @event.description %></p>
      </div>-->
        <h1 class="event-name"><b><%= @event.name %></b></h1>
          <div class="rob" style="color:rgb(180,180,180); width:470px; font-weight:300; font-size:20px; margin-top:16px;">
            October 26
          </div>
        <div class="rob" style="color:rgb(180,180,180); width:470px;  margin-top:16px;   font-family: 'Roboto' !important; font-style: normal;font-weight: 300;font-size:20px;">
            Makati City
          </div>

          <div class="rob" style="color:rgb(180,180,180); max-width:70%px; font-weight:100; font-size:20px; margin-top:16px;">
             <span style="line-height:110%;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed vel facilisis nulla. Quisque posuere interdum quam nec egestas. Pellentesque accumsan eu sapien id congue. Aenean eget elit id magna molestie luctus. Pellentesque eget malesuada tellus, vitae pellentesque odio. Nulla facilisi. Nunc vulputate mi vitae euismod feugiat. Donec sed egestas augue. Vestibulum fermentum accumsan ipsum in feugiat. Sed bibendum quam feugiat orci pulvinar, vel volutpat neque viverra. Nulla augue ipsum, hendrerit at viverra et, ultricies quis lectus. Sed eu nibh in arcu mollis dapibus ut ultrices libero. Donec id hendrerit nisi. Nunc vel enim a erat vulputate pulvinar. Vivamus semper malesuada arcu.</span>

          </div>
          <a class="jb" style=""><center>Join</center></a>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="row" style="min-height: 760px; border:solid 0px; margin-top:10px; background-color:transparent;">

    <div id="map" class="col-md-8" style=" height: 560px;">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4" style=" height: 560px; background-color: #A02A26;    background-clip: padding-box; border-left: 10px solid transparent;">
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
  <p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

  <p>
    <strong>Name:</strong>
    <%= @event.name %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Description:</strong>
    <%= @event.description %> <br>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Start date:</strong>
    <%= @event.start_date %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>End date:</strong>
    <%= @event.end_date %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Address:</strong>
    <%= @event.address %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Website:</strong>
    <%= @event.website %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Organizer:</strong>
    <%= @event.user %>
  </p>

  <% if @attendee_count == 1 %>
    <%= @attendee_count %> Attendee 
  <% else %>
    <%= @attendee_count %> Attendees
  <% end %>

  <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <% if @event.user.id == current_user.id %>
      <%= link_to 'Edit', edit_event_path(@event) %> |
    <% else %>
      <% if @attended.empty? %>
        <%= link_to 'Join', join_event_path(@event.id), :style=>"color:black;"%>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to 'Leave', leave_event_path(@event.id)%>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>

  <%= link_to 'Back', events_path %>
<footer class="footer" style="margin-top:120px">


  <h6 style="color:white;">About us | Terms and Condition | Copyright 2015</h6>
</footer>

<script src="//maps.google.com/maps/api/js?v=3.18&sensor=false&client=&key=&libraries=geometry&language=&hl=&region="></script> 
<script src="//google-maps-utility-library-v3.googlecode.com/svn/tags/markerclustererplus/2.0.14/src/markerclusterer_packed.js"></script>
<script src='//google-maps-utility-library-v3.googlecode.com/svn/tags/infobox/1.1.9/src/infobox_packed.js' type='text/javascript'></script> <!-- only if you need custom infoboxes -->
  
<script type="text/javascript">
handler = Gmaps.build('Google');
handler.buildMap({ provider: {}, internal: {id: 'map'}}, function(){
  markers = handler.addMarkers(<%=raw @hash.to_json %>);
  handler.bounds.extendWith(markers);
  handler.fitMapToBounds();
  handler.getMap().setZoom(17);
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
